on-arrival: {!
if (Q.rb_strength) {
    Q.rb_strength_2 = Q.rb_strength.toFixed(1);
}
if (Q.rfb_strength) {
    Q.rfb_strength_2 = Q.rfb_strength.toFixed(1);
}
if (Q.sh_strength) {
    Q.sh_strength_2 = Q.sh_strength.toFixed(1);
}
if (Q.sa_strength) {
    Q.sa_strength_2 = Q.sa_strength.toFixed(1);
}
!}

= Organizations

Most parties have associated or allied organizations, be that newspapers, think tanks or even paramilitaries.

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="These organizations advocate socialism and workers' emancipation. They are generally aligned with us and other socialist groups.">Socialist Organizations</span>!} Strength: [+ rga_org_2 +] thousand

Socialist outreach: [+ rga_org_militancy : militancy +]

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="These radical organizations advocate social change and revolution, often through violent means. They are sympathetic to the general far left and some of the communists in our party.">Far Left Organizations</span>!} Strength: [+ far_left_org_strength_2 +] thousand

Far-Left outreach: [+ far_left_org_militancy : militancy +]

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="These organizations can be considered the DoR's establishment. They are generally loyal to the right-wing parties.">Conservative Organizations</span>!} Strength: [+ conservative_media_strength_2 +] thousand

Conservative outreach: [+ conservative_org_militancy : militancy +]

{!<span class="tooltip-text" title="Right now, the far-right organizations are practically irrelevant, though we should probably keep an eye on them.">Far Right Media</span>!} Strength: [+ far_right_org_strength_2 +] thousand

Far-Right outreach: [+ far_right_org_militancy : militancy +]

